1436
01:02:31,781 --> 01:02:34,817
Or will Chef Jong-won

1437
01:02:34,884 --> 01:02:36,919
win against Hyun-suk

1438
01:02:36,986 --> 01:02:40,790
and secure his position
as the rising star?

1439
01:02:40,857 --> 01:02:42,859
Who did Keun-suk choose?

1440
01:02:42,925 --> 01:02:44,293
Which chef is it?

1441
01:02:44,360 --> 01:02:46,996
Whose show did you prefer?

1442
01:02:47,063 --> 01:02:49,832
-Ugh.
-Who did Keun-suk choose?

1443
01:02:50,666 --> 01:02:51,801
Who is it?

1444
01:02:54,470 --> 01:02:57,006
CHEF CHOI HYUN-SUK'S
ROE TRIO WINS

1445
01:02:57,073 --> 01:02:58,541
Choi Hyun-suk!

1446
01:02:58,608 --> 01:03:00,076
HYUN-SUK CONTINUES
TO STAND UNDEFEATED

1447
01:03:00,143 --> 01:03:02,578
-Choi Hyun-suk.
-Yes.

1448
01:03:02,645 --> 01:03:04,313
That was so…

1449
01:03:07,617 --> 01:03:08,951
