I wanted to see in this match.

1456
01:03:26,235 --> 01:03:32,108
That was my only preference.
I can't dare to evaluate who's better.

1457
01:03:32,175 --> 01:03:33,876
It was hard to choose one.

1458
01:03:35,711 --> 01:03:38,181
He becomes the only first place.

1459
01:03:38,247 --> 01:03:40,483
He continues his undefeated record.

1460
01:03:40,550 --> 01:03:42,485
Choi Hyun-suk wins all four rounds.

1461
01:03:42,552 --> 01:03:43,786
Choi Hyun-suk's return!

1462
01:03:43,853 --> 01:03:45,955
Don't push out your chest like that.

1463
01:03:46,022 --> 01:03:48,291
He successfully takes his fourth win!

1464
01:03:48,357 --> 01:03:49,926
"THIS WILL BE THE BIGGEST MATCH
OF THE SHOW"

1465
01:03:49,992 --> 01:03:50,993
A QUOTE BY CHOI HYUN-SUK

1466
01:03:51,060 --> 01:03:52,195
That was amazing.

1467
01:03:52,261 --> 01:03:56,532
And next, the order is,
"I won't cry even if it's spicy."

1468
01:03:56,599 --> 01:04:00,736
You'll have to cook for Keun-suk,
who's good at eating spicy food.

1469
01:04:00,803 --> 01:04:05,508
The eldest chef of <i>Chef & My Fridge</i>,
Chef Lee Yeon-bok, born in 1959.

1470
01:04:05,575 --> 01:04:10,246
The youngest chef of <i>Chef & My Fridge</i>,
Chef Kwon Sung-jun, born in 1995.

1471
01:04:10,313 --> 01:04:11,414
Nice symmetry.

1472
01:04:11,480 --> 01:04:13,416
-It's 59 and 95.
-It's 59 and 95.

1473
01:04:13,482 --> 01:04:15,651
This is 1959 versus 1995.

1474
01:04:15,718 --> 01:04:17,553
Chef Sung-jun may look older,

1475
01:04:17,620 --> 01:04:21,257
-but he's still the youngest here.
-He is.

1476
01:04:22,391 --> 01:04:25,328
Here's something Chef Sung-jun said.

1477
01:04:25,394 --> 01:04:28,464
"I want to fight against Chef Yeon-bok.

1478
01:04:28,531 --> 01:04:30,533
I'll win against
the leader of <i>Chef & My Fridge</i>

1479
01:04:30,600 --> 01:04:32,802
